policy.Description: This policy is on a deprecation path. See documentation for guidance: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/elasticbeanstalk/latest/dg/iam-servicerole.html. AWS Elastic Beanstalk Service role policy which grants permissions to create & manage resources (i.e.: AutoScaling, EC2, S3, CloudFormation, ELB, etc.) on your behalf.
